reviews.text: I always go there for happy hour and seldom for dinner. But I have to say they have a very friendly team and we always have a good time there. And the oysters there is always good and food is good
Delicious food. Oysters are served properly and very fresh. Service is excellent
The steak served for lunch is good value
Nice staff,  good food

I hear people talk about the Codfather quite often.  Maybe I was expecting more but it was just ok.  They did mess up our meals but they had no issue remaking them.  I will be back sometime but will try other things on the menu.  Service was top notch though, really friendly and helpful.
